2011_March 9 
Inception is exactly what people thought it was going to be. It was a
hybrid of James Bond and the Matrix and even the Dark Knight. It had
the epic feeling of the Dark Knight, visual appeal of the Matrix, the
action from James Bond results in Christopher Nolan&#x27;s Inception.<br /><br />This movie has the epic scale feeling you regularly get in Sci-Fi
action movies, like the Star Wars trilogy, the Matrix like what was
said before, District 9 and AVATAR but without any aliens in it.<br /><br />Inception is an Sci-Fi action film set within the architecture of the
mind, Christopher Nolan said so himself. I don&#x27;t like going on about
the plot with these reviews regularly, but here&#x27;s the summary: <br /><br />It has to be seen to be believed.
